cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper proposes a method for defect detection in automated fiber placement using image segmentation and deep neural networks. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The use of artificially generated training data and probabilistic graphical models suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the application of the method to composite materials suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
